  <chunk id="54ebc03fe88092d143f0758472adf54252d6c224.c4" text="Conclusion: These results suggest that intracellular fat accumulation in HCV cell culture induces ER stress, defective Jak-Stat signaling, and attenuates the antiviral response, thus providing an explanation to the clinical observation regarding how hepatocellular steatosis influences IFN-α response in CHC.">
